the day it started he didnt really know that much about it 
mrs hallberg said 
mrs hallberg said she hopes to stay in saudia arabia where the 
family has lived for seven years 
you make good benefits and we ended up liking it she said 
for some the arrival of thousands of american troops in the 
peaceful country represented the end of an era in which foreigners 
lived a sheltered comfortable existence mixing mainly among 
themselves 
ive been here nine years and now i dont know what i am going 
to do said james green a briton with a photographic studio in 
