at least 53 people have been killed and more than 300 wounded since 
thursday so far only armed police have patrolled in soweto 
this strong contingent will do everything possible to stop the 
senseless violence van der merwe said in a statement 
its a very tense situation theres a lot of tension and 
people are arming themselves one witness said 
officials put the total dead at 205 in clashes that began sunday 
