stemming from an attack on two male joggers in the park 
the three were ordered remanded to jail without bail each faced 
from to five to 10 years in prison on the rape count alone they 
were to be sentenced as juvenile offenders on sept 11 
the woman was jogging through the northern end of the park when 
she was attacked she was dragged about 70 feet into the woods 
gangraped and bashed repeatedly with a brick and pipe 
